title House Tile(initial)

user->UI: Click Spin
UI->logic: Spin message
logic->logic: compute roll
logic->logic: land on house tile
logic->logic: check if player owns any houses
logic->UI: pass 2(3) options to UI
user->UI: choose action
UI->logic: inform logic of decision
alt Do nothing
    
else Sell
    logic->logic: get list of users houses
    logic->UI: pass list to UI
    user->UI: select house to sell
    UI->logic: pass on selection
    logic->UI: request spin to set price
    user->UI: Click spin
    UI->logic: Spin message
    logic->logic: compute roll
    logic->logic: sell card
else Buy
    logic->logic: get top cards from deck
    logic->UI: pass options to UI
    user->UI: select a house
    UI->logic: pass on selection
    alt Player can afford
        logic->logic: buy house
    else Player cannot afford
        logic->logic: options are - loan or do nothing
        logic->UI: pass options to UI
        user->UI: select a option
        UI->logic: pass on selection
        alt Loan
            logic->logic: take out loan
            logic->logic: buy house
        else Do nothing
            
        end
    end
end
logic->UI: turn over/status update
user->UI: acknowledge turn end
UI->logic: ack. message
logic->logic: next player
